relation: Symmetry - #11 Thomas is a little jumpy to be a fireman... Yay, another abnormally long comic. :D

Fan Art of the Week winner! 10 Jul 2006 I didn't realize it, but I don't think I have any Earthbound fanart posted. :O Unacceptable! Can't say this is my best work - the lines are messy, but I guess it's better than nothing. :)
After realizing I'd have to draw the Magypsies ( sp? ) in Symmetry eventually, I thought maybe practicing them once or twice would be a good idea. I think I'll definatley stick with "once".
Following the pattern of Chapter based pictures, this one was based on Chapter 4. My pencils started to get too small to use, so DCMC looks a little sloppy...:(
Symmetry - #10 Poor Thomas. One fireman can only do so much.
